/default/strip/false/crop/5000x2813+0+0/resize/600/quality/85/format/jpeg/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fa7%2F73%2Fc7f9e3b443f19ee10e53a522867c%2Flk-dating-irl-1-gettyimages-2077013533-copy.jpg 600w, https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/5000x2813+0+0/resize/800/quality/85/format/jpeg/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fa7%2F73%2Fc7f9e3b443f19ee10e53a522867c%2Flk-dating-irl-1-gettyimages-2077013533-copy.jpg 800w, https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/5000x2813+0+0/resize/900/quality/85/format/jpeg/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fa7%2F73%2Fc7f9e3b443f19ee10e53a522867c%2Flk-dating-irl-1-gettyimages-2077013533-copy.jpg 900w, https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/5000x2813+0+0/resize/1200/quality/85/format/jpeg/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fa7%2F73%2Fc7f9e3b443f19ee10e53a522867c%2Flk-dating-irl-1-gettyimages-2077013533-copy.jpg 1200w, https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/5000x2813+0+0/resize/1600/quality/85/format/jpeg/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fa7%2F73%2Fc7f9e3b443f19ee10e53a522867c%2Flk-dating-irl-1-gettyimages-2077013533-copy.jpg 1600w, https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/5000x2813+0+0/resize/1800/quality/85/format/jpeg/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fa7%2F73%2Fc7f9e3b443f19ee10e53a522867c%2Flk-dating-irl-1-gettyimages-2077013533-copy.jpg 1800w" data-template="https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/5000x2813+0+0/resize/{width}/quality/{quality}/format/{format}/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fa7%2F73%2Fc7f9e3b443f19ee10e53a522867c%2Flk-dating-irl-1-gettyimages-2077013533-copy.jpg" sizes="(min-width: 1025px) 650px, calc(100vw - 30px)" class="img" type="image/jpeg" /&gt;             &lt;img src="https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/5000x2813+0+0/resize/1100/quality/50/format/jpeg/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fa7%2F73%2Fc7f9e3b443f19ee10e53a522867c%2Flk-dating-irl-1-gettyimages-2077013533-copy.jpg" data-template="https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/5000x2813+0+0/resize/{width}/quality/{quality}/format/{format}/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fa7%2F73%2Fc7f9e3b443f19ee10e53a522867c%2Flk-dating-irl-1-gettyimages-2077013533-copy.jpg" class="img" alt="Illustration of two people. One is standing, facing the viewer, the other is walking toward the left side of the frame. They both have smartphones in their hands, but they look up at each other and make eye contact. They stand in front of a large illustrated heart and are surrounded by smaller hearts, symbolizing the concept of dating and flirting in real life. " loading="lazy" /&gt;         &lt;/picture&gt; &lt;/div&gt; &lt;div class="credit-caption"&gt;     &lt;div class="caption-wrap"&gt;         &lt;div class="caption" aria-label="Image caption"&gt;         &lt;/div&gt;       &lt;/div&gt;       &lt;/div&gt;    &lt;/div&gt;    &lt;p&gt;Flirting in real life is becoming a lost art. At least that is what confidence coach Regina Bonds thinks. If talking to a cute stranger makes your palms sweat, but you want to find a love interest without dating apps, Bonds has some advice &lt;a href="https://www.npr.org/2025/07/18/nx-s1-5420731/flirting-in-real-life" target="_blank"&gt;to overcome common fears&lt;/a&gt; about approaching a romantic interest in the wild. &lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;   &lt;ul class="edTag"&gt;&lt;li&gt;❤️ If you are too nervous to talk to someone because you don't think you'd be a good romantic partner, build up your self-esteem. Try reciting a positive mantra in front of a mirror about your worth.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;❤️ A simple way to show interest is to make eye contact. If they look back at you and smile, that is a promising sign.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;❤️ There are no rules to dating. Don't be afraid to strike up a conversation first and if you don't know what to say, start by giving them a compliment.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;   &lt;p&gt;For more advice on how to be confident while flirting in person, &lt;a href="https://one.npr.org/?sharedMediaId=nx-s1-5420731:x" target="_blank"&gt;listen to this episode of NPR's &lt;em&gt;Life Kit&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/a&gt;. Subscribe to &lt;a href="https://www.npr.org/newsletter/life-kit" target="_blank"&gt;the&lt;em&gt; Life Kit &lt;/em&gt;newsletter&lt;/a&gt; for expert advice on love, money, relationships and more.&lt;/p&gt;       &lt;h3 class="edTag"&gt;Weekend picks&lt;/h3&gt;   &lt;div id="resg-s1-77763" class="bucketwrap image large"&gt;             &lt;div     class="imagewrap has-source-dimensions"     data-crop-type=""     style="         --source-width: 2560;         --source-height: 1440;     " &gt;         &lt;picture&gt;             &lt;source srcset="https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/2560x1440+0+0/resize/400/quality/85/format/webp/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F18%2F55%2Fef6efd044e5085e7f311ead656e6%2Fsorry-baby-1.jpg 400w, https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/2560x1440+0+0/resize/600/quality/85/format/webp/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F18%2F55%2Fef6efd044e5085e7f311ead656e6%2Fsorry-baby-1.jpg 600w, https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/2560x1440+0+0/resize/800/quality/85/format/webp/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F18%2F55%2Fef6efd044e5085e7f311ead656e6%2Fsorry-baby-1.jpg 800w, https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/2560x1440+0+0/resize/900/quality/85/format/webp/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F18%2F55%2Fef6efd044e5085e7f311ead656e6%2Fsorry-baby-1.jpg 900w, https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/2560x1440+0+0/resize/1200/quality/85/format/webp/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F18%2F55%2Fef6efd044e5085e7f311ead656e6